        "heading": "<h2>Advanced Light Therapy for Androgenetic Alopecia</h2>",
        "text": "<p>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet utilizes the power of low-level light therapy (LLLT), a scientifically-backed technology for treating androgenetic alopecia. It delivers a precise combination of red light and laser therapy to stimulate dormant hair follicles and support the natural hair growth cycle.</p>",
